      "date": "2013-08-17 15:59:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el5/i686: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/2000283e-0756-11e3-927d-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
