        "subject": "LU-3767 ldiskfs: \"force_over_24tb\" mount option to \"64tb\"",
        "message": "LU-3767 ldiskfs: \"force_over_24tb\" mount option to \"64tb\"\n\nChange the \"force_over_24tb\" mount option to\n\"force_over_64tb\" and rename the ext4-force_over_24tb-*.patch\nto ext4-force_over_64tb-*.patch after testing and validating\nthe 64TB LUN.\n\nThe maximum LUN size for b1_8 was increased from 16TB to\n24TB in http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/589/. This patch tries\nto increase the max LUN size to 64TB.\n\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I84a5e2de77e4713b1b167978da1da6ecfff2a7dd\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b1_8"
    }
